{"tid":133010,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[新武術大學] 科大生嗌莊變武鬥　官揶揄：讀武術呀？","createTime":"2017-02-24T08:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T16:11:04.000Z","uid":67284,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1c9d87ed7d8a21bb04575a8ab93f632ca41811d8","tid":133010,"uid":67284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T08:58:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170224/mobile/bkn-20170224131851141-0224_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170224%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170224131851141-0224_00822_001.html&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHExv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=8e068be0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170224/mobile/bkn-20170224131851141-0224_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n去年2月26日，香港科技大學發生校園暴力事件，逾百名學生在校園進行「上莊」選舉宣傳活動期間，有人先口角繼而動武，事後有學生需送院治理。事隔一年，一名科大男生被控兩項襲擊致造成身體傷害，今在觀塘法院提堂，辯方申請暫時毋須答辯，案件押後至下月10日再訊，期間被告獲准以現金5000港元保釋。 <br />\n<br />\n報稱科大二年級生的被告莊鈞絡(20歲)今日由當值律師代表，辯方表示被告打算聘請私人大狀，亦需時翻閱控方證據，申請押後答辯。裁判官問被告「讀咩㗎？」辯方律師指被告讀科大，官澄清意指是被告讀甚麼學科，更揶揄「我係問佢讀咩？武術呀？」辯方透露他修讀電子工程。 <br />\n<br />\nust原來先係真武鬥大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"256016a0dcbb2a68cde06f4a49da4aafa92e59f8","tid":133010,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T08:59:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14f3b8ddac46f6ba2b7eec67b7be462fb683f75","tid":133010,"uid":60015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T09:00:15.000Z","msg":"On9嘢唔想理"},{"pid":"9b321362dc16c135eee20f36f8f0db008ee20fa1","tid":133010,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T09:00:48.000Z","msg":"留案底就好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搏盡無悔"},{"pid":"735e922